      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JACKPOT JUNIOR (1) racing well without winning, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 3rd in a Grade 4/5 on April 5 over 407m at this track behind How's Warren beaten 4 lengths (24.32). Unbeaten from this box in two starts. Well placed and gets his chance. DOZEN DONUTS (7) jumped from this box last time and also the same course and distance to score a Grade 6 win (24.10). Leading player again. CLEAR BLUE SKY (8) missed the frame last time but just three runs back was a strong Grade 5 winner (23.99) at this track over 407m. Has the ability and expected to do much better. BOONIE'S BELLA (2) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
